1000351-Herrmann1">46. <span class="element-citation">Herrmann T, Guntert P, Wuthrich K. Protein NMR structure determination with automated NOE-identification in the NOESY spectra using the new software ATNOS. <span><span class="ref-journal">J Biomol NMR. </span>2002;<span class="ref-vol">24</span>:171\xe2\x80\x93189.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/12522306" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2654722&amp;issue-id=176716&amp;journal-id=349&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=J+Biomol+NMR&amp;title=Protein+NMR+structure+determination+with+automated+NOE-identification+in+the+NOESY+spectra+using+the+new+software+ATNOS.&amp;author=T+Herrmann&amp;author=P+Guntert&amp;author=K+Wuthrich&amp;volume=24&amp;publication_year=2002&amp;pages=171-189&amp;pmid=12522306&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2654722&amp;issue-id=176716&amp;journal-id=349&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></div><div class="ref-cit-blk half_rhythm" id="ppat.1000351-Guntert1">47. <span class="element-citation">Guntert P. Automated NMR structure calculation with CYANA. <span><span class="ref-journal">Methods Mol Biol. </span>2004;<span class="ref-vol">278</span>:353\xe2\x80\x93378.</span> [<a href="/pubmed/15318003" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=pubmed&amp;article-id=2654722&amp;issue-id=176716&amp;journal-id=349&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Entrez%7CPubMed%7CRecord">PubMed</a>] <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Methods+Mol+Biol&amp;title=Automated+NMR+structure+calculation+with+CYANA.&amp;author=P+Guntert&amp;volume=278&amp;publication_year=2004&amp;pages=353-378&amp;pmid=15318003&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=2654722&amp;issue-id=176716&amp;journal-id=349&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;T